description:
Frappe allows you to personalize your workspace with "Blocks." Click the "+" button on the top right to add blocks.
Choose from various block types like "Cards" for quick access to frequently used documents, "Charts" to visualize data, "Shortcuts" for one-click navigation, and more.
Arrange and resize blocks to create a layout that suits your workflow.
Video Suggestion: Search for "[YouTube] Frappe Workspace Customization" to see how to add and manage blocks.
name: Customize Your Workspace
title: Customize Your Workspace
